graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container orchestration| K8s[OpenShift/Kubernetes 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow execution| Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Embedded namespace-scoped]
    DSPO -->|metadata persistence| DB[MariaDB 10.3+ or<br/>External MySQL DB]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| Storage[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Minio or AWS S3]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|cert management| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|pipeline submission| Workbenches[Workbenches/Notebooks]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring]
    DSPO -->|deployment| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster CR]

    %% Optional Integrations
    DSPO -.->|model deployment| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService]

    %% Component details
    K8s -->|provides| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 6443/TCP]
    K8s -->|provides| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>TLS termination]
    K8s -->|provides| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Authentication]
    K8s -->|provides| ServiceCert[service-cert controller<br/>Auto TLS rotation]

    Argo -->|executes| Workflows[Workflow CRs<br/>argoproj.io/v1alpha1]
    Argo -->|creates| WorkflowPods[Workflow Pods<br/>Pipeline tasks]

    DB -->|stores| PipelineMetadata[Pipeline metadata<br/>runs, experiments, artifacts]
    Storage -->|stores| Artifacts[Pipeline artifacts<br/>models, datasets]

    Dashboard -->|manages| Pipelines[Pipeline CRUD operations]
    Workbenches -->|uses| KFPSDK[KFP SDK<br/>Pipeline development]

    %% Reverse dependencies (who depends on DSPO)
    DataScientists[Data Scientists] -->|uses| DSPO
    MLWorkflows[ML Workflows] -->|orchestrated by| DSPO

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DB fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Storage fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
